n and display! I'm now testing.\n\n\n**Adding Loading Indicators**\n\nI'm now incorporating loading states! I've added a loading indicator using skeleton panels to `/app/portal/governance/page.tsx` for a more user-friendly experience during data fetching. I'm ensuring a smooth transition. I've also incorporated an error handling display.\n\n\n"}}
